[Description] Bbmail is a mail-checker with a Blackbox look and feel. Although it was designed for Blackbox it should also work with any other Window Manager. It is highly configurable and can be placed in the Blackbox Slit. Bbmail is a part of bbtools, a number Blackbox applets already including bbdate, bbsload and bbppp.
[Homepage] http://bbtools.windsofstorm.net/
